channel.title: Project fury
channel.description:
As many of you may know, me Flamed fury1, fedexer and some others are soon starting a massive server project. It will be a project like no other, we are planning on making a very very big updated version of project 16 v6-7 adding many custom features that are made souly by us, this will be a very very hard job over the next few months and in the end will be hosted/ sold off on various forums. If you would like to take part in this project you are very welcome if youre application is accepted. You can only fill out one application per person.
The following jobs we have open:
1. Someone who can customize a client and embead in a webpage.
2. Someone who would like to add custom ints and add-ons to duel arena.
3. Someone who can follow tuts step by step no errors.
4. Somebody who would like to advertise the finished product when it is complete.
Please could you fill out the following application:
[u][b]How would our project benefit from your help?[/b][/u]
[u][b]A previous peice of custom coding you have made. (Has to be yours!)[/b][/u]
[u][b]What job you would like to take part in.[/b][/u]
[b][u]Moparisthebest name:[/u][/b]
[u][b]Any other known coding languages e.g C++ [/b][/u]
Please post your application here, and no spam or questions please! Only post app's here nothing else. Thanks
[size=1pt]Disclaimer: This job doesn't pay in anyway.[/size] ~Project Fury~
